# 🚀 Commerce Data Platform

## 📌 Project Overview

The Commerce Data Platform is an end-to-end Data Engineering project designed to transform raw retail transaction data into business-ready insights.

Using Medallion Architecture (Bronze → Silver → Gold), the project demonstrates data ingestion, data cleaning, dimensional modelling, warehousing, SQL analytics, and business reporting.

The solution processes over 1 million retail transactions from the Online Retail II dataset and delivers analytics-ready datasets for reporting and decision-making.

---

## 🏗️ Architecture

```text
Online Retail II Dataset
          │
          ▼
     Bronze Layer
          │
          ▼
     Silver Layer
          │
          ▼
   Data Warehouse
          │
          ▼
      Gold Layer
          │
          ▼
    SQL Analytics
          │
          ▼
   Business Insights
```

---

## 🥉 Bronze Layer

Raw data ingestion layer.

### Source

- Online Retail II Dataset (Kaggle)

### Output

```text
bronze/
└── online_retail.parquet
```

### Purpose

- Store raw source data
- Maintain data lineage
- Preserve original records

---

## 🥈 Silver Layer

Data quality and transformation layer.

### Data Quality Operations

- Removed null customer records
- Removed duplicate transactions
- Removed invalid quantities
- Removed invalid prices
- Generated Revenue column

### Output

```text
silver/
└── sales_cleaned.parquet
```

---

## 🏛️ Data Warehouse

A dimensional data model was implemented using a Star Schema.

### Fact Table

#### fact_sales

| Column |
|----------|
| Invoice |
| InvoiceDate |
| customer_key |
| product_key |
| Quantity |
| Price |
| Revenue |

---

### Dimension Tables

#### dim_customer

| Column |
|----------|
| customer_key |
| Customer ID |
| Country |

#### dim_product

| Column |
|----------|
| product_key |
| StockCode |
| Description |

#### dim_date

| Column |
|----------|
| date_key |
| Date |
| Month |
| Quarter |
| Year |

---

## 🥇 Gold Layer

Business-ready analytical datasets.

### Outputs

```text
gold/

├── monthly_sales.csv
├── country_sales.csv
├── customer_metrics.csv
└── product_metrics.csv
```

### Metrics Generated

- Monthly Revenue Trends
- Revenue by Country
- Customer Performance
- Product Performance

